methods.name: UFGVehicleCollisionBoxComponent
methods.comment: Sets default values for this component's properties

properties.name: mFudgeFactor
properties.comment: Multiplier for velocity change with all impacts.

properties.name: mAddedZVelocityFactor
properties.comment: Added Z Velocity multiplier. DOES NOT specify how much velocity. This number should be small 0.0-1.0 range

properties.name: mMaxAddedZVelocity
properties.comment: The maximum Z velocity that can be added on a collision.

properties.name: mMaxCollisionVelocity
properties.comment: The maximum velocity that can be added on a collision.

properties.name: mMinVelocityForAddedZ
properties.comment: The minimum velocity required for any fudged Z values to take effect. This helps when player just runs against the vehicle.
